    • RejectedExecution

      public void RejectedExecution(Runnable task, SequenceCachedPool executor)
      从接口复制的说明: rejectedExecutionHandler
      When SequenceCachedPoolis subject to a capacity limit, theSequenceCachedPool method is called. This can happen when there are no more threads or queue slots available, either because their boundaries will be exceeded, or when the executor is closed.



      当 SequenceCachedPool 受到容满限制时， SequenceCachedPool 调用的方法。没有更多的线程或队列槽可用时，可能会发生这种情况，因为它们的边界将被超出，或者在执行程序关闭时。

      In the absence of other alternatives, the method may throw an unchecked RejectedExecutionException, which will be propagated to the caller of execute.

      在没有其他替代方法的情况下，该方法可能会抛出未经检查的 RejectedExecutionException，该异常将传播到 execute 的调用方

      指定者:
      RejectedExecution 在接口中 rejectedExecutionHandler
      参数:
      task - the runnable task requested to be executed
      executor - the executor attempting to execute this task
